<item>
            <title>[GROOVY-2180] LoaderConfiguration is broken for relative paths</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/GROOVY-2180</link>
                <project id="12318123" key="GROOVY">Groovy</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In Grails we have a config like this:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;	# load project resources
	load ${base.dir}/lib/*.jar
	load ${base.dir}/plugins/*/lib/*.jar
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The base.dir variable can sometimes be just &quot;.&quot; which for a relative path. However a recent change to LoaderConfiguration has broken this. The problem is here:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;177:   Matcher m = pattern.matcher(getSlashyPath(file.getAbsolutePath()));
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It should be the following to allow relative paths:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;177:   Matcher m = pattern.matcher(getSlashyPath(file.getPath()));
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
